description:

Compatible with Canon NB-4L batteries, CB-2LV chargers and these cameras or camcorders:

ELPH 300 HS
ELPH 310 HS

Powershot SD960 IS
PowerShot TX1
VIXIA mini
title: STK's Canon NB-4L Battery 1400mHa for Canon ELPH 330 HS, ELPH 300 HS, VIXIA mini, ELPH 100 HS, ELPH 310 HS, Powershot SD1400 IS, SD750, SD1000, SD600, SD1100 IS, SD630, SD400, SD450, SD780, CB-2LV
